  "general_tips": [
    "Sweepers exist only at rare — go-wide strategies are safer than usual.",
    "Combat tricks are exceptional in MKM; respect open mana and play around On the Job, The Chase Is On, and Auspicious Arrival.",
    "Green is the splash-enabler thanks to its mana fixers — multicolor is on the table.",
    "Disguise creatures have Ward 2 — keep that in mind when sizing your removal.",
    "Tempo matters more than pure card quality; pressure early and finish before the opponent stabilizes."
  ]
}